enumerations.name: FMFeatureSelectionState
enumerations.note: Defines how a particular FMFeature contributes to a FMFSelectionSet. Aggregated by FMFeatureSelection.state

literals.name: deselected
literals.description:
The feature is excluded from the selection.
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=0

literals.name: selected
literals.description:
The feature is included in the selection.
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=1

literals.name: undecided
literals.description:
It is not yet decided whether the feature shall be included into or excluded from the selection.
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=2
